@nelsonsang I agree. We know Bud is a switch hitter that hits people w/ shots they don't see. I could see Canelo biting down on his mouthpiece in the later rounds. Crawford will be right there and Canelo's head movement is incredible. I think Bud will turn Canelo all night and take his right hand away. What a great style fight. 
FYI- Crawford is a former wrestler. Very strong on the inside. This fight can go so many ways. I could see Canelo with a knockout or Bud beating him down over several rounds w/ a stoppage. I think Bud knows his body. He looks strong. 
I love Both fighters.

